{"id":1966,"date":"2024-03-11T23:21:07","date_gmt":"2024-03-11T22:21:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/roos.twietcreativemarketing.nu\/?page_id=1966"},"modified":"2024-10-28T10:44:53","modified_gmt":"2024-10-28T09:44:53","slug":"about-us","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/roos.twietcreativemarketing.nu\/about-us\/","title":{"rendered":"About us"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wpb-content-wrapper\">[vc_row inner_container=&#8221;true&#8221; no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;background-color:#0000ff; padding: 0% 6% 2% 6%;&#8221;]<div  class=\"x-visibility x-hidden-desktop\" ><hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 25px 0 0 0;\"><\/div><h2  class=\"h-custom-headline h3\" ><span><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Divd.fund<\/span><\/span><\/h2><p><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">We stand at the forefront of a mission dedicated to fortifying the digital realm. Our non-profit foundation is committed to making the internet safer, more robust, and secure. Through our funding program, we support impactful initiatives that contribute to a better online world. This can only be made possible through gifts and donations of like-minded individuals, businesses, and organizations who understand the importance of a secure cyber future and believe in the strength of our community-driven fundraising foundation.<\/span><\/p>\n<hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 40px 0 0 0;\">[\/vc_column][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;&#8221; style=&#8221;padding: 0% 0% 0% 0%;&#8221;]<div  class=\"x-visibility x-hidden-phone\" ><hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 40px 0 0 0;\"><img decoding=\"async\"  class=\"x-img\" style=\"padding: 20%\" src=\"https:\/\/roos.twietcreativemarketing.nu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/brand-DIVD-fund.png\" ><\/div>[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row inner_container=&#8221;true&#8221; no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;padding: 0% 0% 0% 0%;&#8221;]<div  class=\"x-visibility x-hidden-phone\" ><\/div>[\/vc_column][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;&#8221; style=&#8221;background-color:white; padding: 0% 6% 2% 6%;&#8221;]<div  class=\"x-visibility x-hidden-desktop\" ><hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 25px 0 0 0;\"><\/div><h2  class=\"h-custom-headline h3\" ><span>How it <span style=\"color: #fdd734;\">all<\/span> began.<\/span><\/h2><p>Since 2019, enthusiastic hackers have been scanning the internet and reporting vulnerabilities under the banner of the Dutch Institute of Vulnerability Disclosure (DIVD). With the number of potential victims continually rising, notifying them of the possible risks became a crucial priority. In the course of their work, researchers often gained new insights or came up with innovative ideas. However, due to a lack of time and funding, many of these ideas remained undeveloped. To address this, the independent fundraising foundation DIVD.fund was established, providing funding for promising projects aimed at making the internet a safer place.<\/p>\n<hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 40px 0 0 0;\">[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;background-color:white; padding: 0% 4% 2% 4%;&#8221;]<div  class=\"x-visibility x-hidden-phone\" ><h2  class=\"h-custom-headline mtn ptl mbs h3\" ><span>How do we <span style=\"color: #fdd734;\">make<\/span> a difference?<\/span><\/h2><p>We are dedicated to creating a secure and healthy internet for everyone. Our mission drives us to stimulate and finance innovative ideas and projects that enhance digital security. We believe that when individuals, companies, and organizations unite with a shared commitment to making the internet safer, we can achieve remarkable outcomes. By connecting innovation, knowledge, capital, and talent, we cultivate a synergy that enables us to tackle ambitious goals and empower not just individuals but also the broader community and society. Together, we are transforming the digital world into a safer place for all.<\/p>\n<p>By donating to DIVD.fund, you play an essential role in helping us fund groundbreaking projects and initiatives that will make a lasting impact.<\/p>\n<\/div>[vc_row_inner inner_container=&#8221;true&#8221; no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column_inner fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;]<hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 20px 0 0 0;\"><a  class=\"x-btn x-btn-pill x-btn-regular x-btn-block\"  href=\"https:\/\/roos.twietcreativemarketing.nu\/fundraising\/\"     data-options=\"thumbnail: ''\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">I WANT TO DONATE!<\/span><\/a><hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 40px 0 0 0;\">[\/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/3&#8243;][\/vc_column_inner][\/vc_row_inner][\/vc_column][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;&#8221; style=&#8221;padding: 0% 0% 0% 0%;&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;background-color:#0000ff; padding: 0% 4% 2% 4%;&#8221;]<h2  class=\"h-custom-headline mtn ptl mbs h3\" ><span><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">IT IS OUR <span style=\"color: #fdd734;\">MISSION<\/span> TO MAKE THE INTERNET SAFER, HEALTHIER, AND MORE ROBUST FOR EVERYONE.<\/span><\/span><\/h2><hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 40px 0 0 0;\">[\/vc_column][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;padding: 0% 0% 0% 0%;&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;padding: 0% 0% 0% 0%;&#8221;][\/vc_column][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;background-color:white; padding: 0% 4% 2% 4%;&#8221;]<h2  class=\"h-custom-headline mtn ptl mbs h3\" ><span>Vision.<\/span><\/h2><p>DIVD.fund believes in the power of talent, the quality of the individual, and the combined strength of people working together in securing the digital world. Based on a shared mindset and intrinsic drive to make the internet a safer place, DIVD.fund brings together personal growth and joint development. People, businesses, and organizations join us on our mission to connect innovation, knowledge, capital, and talent. The resulting synergy implies no ambition is too large and no goal is unachievable, which strengthens individuals, communities, and society.<\/p>\n<hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 40px 0 0 0;\">[\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;background-color:#0000ff; padding: 0% 4% 2% 4%;&#8221;]<h2  class=\"h-custom-headline mtn ptl mbs h3\" ><span><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">Strategy.<\/span><\/span><\/h2><p><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">\u2022 Establishing and expanding a robust organization<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">\u2022 Offering a learn\/work environment (traineeship\/vacancies)<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">\u2022 Setting up an effective fundraising strategy<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">\u2022 Developing an inclusive funding program<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"color: #ffffff;\">\u2022 Establishing DIVD.fund&#8217;s global presence<\/span><\/p>\n<hr  class=\"x-gap\" style=\"margin: 60px 0 0 0;\">[\/vc_column][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;&#8221; style=&#8221;padding: 0% 0% 0% 0%;&#8221;][\/vc_column][\/vc_row][vc_row inner_container=&#8221;true&#8221; no_margin=&#8221;true&#8221; padding_top=&#8221;0px&#8221; padding_bottom=&#8221;0px&#8221; marginless_columns=&#8221;true&#8221; bg_video=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;mtn&#8221; style=&#8221;&#8221;][vc_column fade_animation_offset=&#8221;45px&#8221; width=&#8221;1\/2&#8243; id=&#8221;&#8221; class=&#8221;&#8221; style=